If the required Book id is 500, then the number of comparisons will be 2, and hence display Collect the book from counter
If the required Book ID is 906, then the number of comparisons will be 5 and hence display Searching and grabbing of book will take some time, Please wait
If the required Book id is 62, then the number of comparisons will be 10 and hence display Searching and grabbing of book will take some time, Please wait
If the required Book id is 875, then the number of comparisons will be 3, and hence display Collect the book from counter
